title: Dyspanic / Enuma Elish (2014)
description:
Dyspanic was founded in 2011 by Alexey Berdnik and Michael Enot. Dyspanic has elements of Progressive Metal, Mathcore, Metalcore, Groove Metal, Nu Metal and Djent. In July 2012 was published the first track Geiger, in which the vocal was performed by Anton Nazarov (Lora Palmer). The track was presented in social networks. In 2014 the band released the first album Enuma Elish.
